Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper deals with image reconstruction using a variational network, which is a common technique in computer vision. 
2. cs.IM (Image and Video Processing) - The paper focuses on reconstructing images from time-of-flight measurements, which is a common problem in image processing. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a machine learning approach to train the variational network for image reconstruction. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper deals with solving a challenging problem of limited-angle computed tomography, which is a common problem in numerical analysis. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with real-time imaging on an ultrasound machine, which can be considered a multimedia application.
